        TurboText   (c) Oxxi

    Many thanks to the programmers of this great programs.

    AM tries to allocate all resources, structures and memory dynamically.
    So the number of entries is only dependent to the amount of free memory.
    All structures will be handled with exec`s lists structures.
    Because of using only 7 entries per entry, the sort and search routins
    may be relatively fast.

    I hope that this doesn`t have too much BUGS.
    I would like to get a lot of mail and tips, gifts , etc...

    I`ve tried to fix all enforcer hits, but if you recognize some new, please
    let me know.

@Endnode

